statements: SELECT * FROM feature_engineering;
SELECT feature_name, data_type FROM feature_engineering;
SELECT * FROM feature_engineering WHERE importance > 0.5;
SELECT feature_name, transformation FROM feature_engineering ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT AVG(importance) AS avg_importance FROM feature_engineering;
SELECT id, feature_name FROM feature_engineering WHERE importance > 0.5 ORDER BY importance DESC;

SELECT feature_name, model_name FROM feature_engineering INNER JOIN feature_model_relationship ON feature_engineering.feature_id = feature_model_relationship.feature_id JOIN predictive_modeling ON feature_model_relationship.model_id = predictive_modeling.model_id ORDER BY feature_name ASC;

SELECT fe.feature_name, pm.model_name FROM feature_engineering fe INNER JOIN feature_model_relationship fmr ON fe.feature_id = fmr.feature_id INNER JOIN predictive_modeling pm ON fmr.model_id = pm.model_id ORDER BY pm.model_name ASC;
